{
  "name": "dct-emachines-q1-2003-lineup",
  "title": "eMachines Q1 2003 Product Lineup",
  "description": "Compact snapshot of the eMachines Q1 2003 desktop product lineup: T1842 ($399 Celeron 1.8 GHz), T2042 ($499 Celeron 2.0 GHz), T2260 ($599 Athlon XP 2200+), and T2460 ($649 Athlon XP 2400+). All ship with 128-256 MB memory, 40-60 GB HDD, CD-ROM or CD-RW/DVD optical, sold direct via www.emachines.com. Documents eMachines' successful sub-$500 value positioning at the bottom of the U.S. consumer PC market, which ultimately led to Gateway's 2004 acquisition of the company.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
